

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Expense Tracker</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #fff;
        }
  
        .header{
              background-color: #ACF6D5;
              display:flex;
              height:65px;
              margin:5px;
             }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #ACF6D5;
         
            width: 100%;
        }
        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: right; 
        }
        .navbar ul li {
            margin: 0 20px;
        }
        .navbar ul li a {
            color: rgb(18, 19, 19);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            text-shadow: #000000;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }


        .hero-section {
           
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 80vh;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-section h2 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #ffcb05;
        }
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-btn {
            background-color: #ff6347;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff4500;
        }
        .features {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .features h3 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .feature-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            width: 30%;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .feature-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        /* Media Queries for responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .feature-card {
                width: 90%;
            }
            .navbar ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .navbar ul li {
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
      <div class="header">
      <div style="margin-left: 30px;margin-top: 5px;">
        <img src="html/moneymind.png" alt="Money Mind Logo" width="300px">
      </div>
        <div class="navbar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about-us">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact-us">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          </div>
    </header>

    <section id="home" class="hero-section">
        <div>
            <h2>Track Your Spending Effortlessly</h2>
            <p>Monitor, analyze, and take control of your finances with ease.</p>
      
            <button class="cta-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/signin'">Start Tracking</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <h3>Why Use Expense Tracker?</h3>
        <div class="feature-cards">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Real-time Monitoring</h4>
                <p>Track your daily, weekly, and monthly expenses with live updates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Custom Categories</h4>
                <p>Personalize your expense categories to match your lifestyle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Visual Reports</h4>
                <p>Generate beautiful charts and reports to analyze your spending patterns.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="privacy-policy" class="footer">
        <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>Your data is safe with us. We respect your privacy and do not share your information with third parties.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="about-us" class="footer">
        <h3>About Us</h3>
        <p>Expense Tracker is dedicated to helping you manage your finances with ease. Our mission is to make budgeting stress-free.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact-us" class="footer">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@expensetracker.com">contact us</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Expense Tracker. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>